{
  "text": "In recent years, there has been an upsurge in the application of low-level laser therapy (LLLT) across several neurologic, dental, ophthalmic, dermatologic disorders, and injuries [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . Furthermore, LLLT has been shown to be an efficacious adjunct therapy for numerous cosmetic procedures, including lipoplasty.",
